You’ve just signed on to join hundreds (maybe thousands?!) of kindred spirits all over the world to celebrate the simple pleasure of a bicycle campout!

We hope you’re already dreaming up the perfect spot to pitch camp after a good day of riding!

Some folks will skip town with a crew they know and love--the travel companions that have weathered many miles together.

Others will invite friends and strangers to camp by bicycle for the first time!

We’ll leave it to you to choose the destination, terrain and the level of challenge.

But we do ask that
  your adventure is self-supported
  and that you *leave no trace*

There will be
Ladies organizing rides for ladies,
Anglers chasing rivers for a weekend of cycling and fly fishing,
Families packing up their kids to bike-camp with toys in tow, and
Shops inviting their customers on a weekend joy ride!

Share your Swift Campout stories by logging into your account at
https://builtbyswift.com/swiftcampout/sign_up

and better yet, drop us a line from the trail!

